&gt;&gt; &gt;                     END
&gt;&gt; &gt;                 END
&gt;&gt; &gt;              END
&gt;&gt; &gt;          NEXT Link
&gt;&gt; &gt;      NEXT Neuron
&gt;&gt; &gt;      FOR EACH Link that fired, set its fired value to TRUE
